      "Max Def Burnt Sienna is the warm-end specialty in the Northgate Climateflex catalog. The granule blend leans toward sienna and terracotta, with deep red and tobacco accents that approximate a true Mediterranean tile look. In direct Florida sun the warmth is unmistakable.",
